Package org.cloudbus.cloudsim.sdn

Class Channel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudbus.cloudsim.sdn.Channel
  • public class Channel
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a channel for transmission of data between switches. It controls sharing of available bandwidth. Relation between Transmission and Channel is the same as Cloudlet and CloudletScheduler, but here we consider only the time shared case, representing a shared channel among different simultaneous package transmissions. This is logical channel. One physical link (class Link) can hold more than one logical channels (class Channel). Channel is directional. It is one way.
    Since:
    CloudSimSDN 1.0
    Author:
    Jungmin Son, Rodrigo N. Calheiros
